<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Event Postponement Notice</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        h2 {
            color: #333;
        }
        p {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #555;
        }
        ul {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
        }
        ul li {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #777;
            text-align: center;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h2>Dear <%= name %>,</h2>
        
        <p>We wanted to inform you that the <strong><%= eventName %></strong>, originally scheduled for <strong><%= originalDate %></strong>, has been postponed.</p>
        
        <p>However, we are pleased to share the updated event details with you:</p>
        
        <ul>
            <li>📅 <strong>Start Time:</strong> <%= startTime %></li>
            <li>⏰ <strong>End Time:</strong> <%= endTime %></li>
        </ul>
        
        <p>Your existing registration remains valid for the rescheduled event, and we look forward to your participation.</p>
        
        <p>We sincerely apologize for any inconvenience this may have caused and truly appreciate your understanding.</p>
        
        
        <p>Best regards</p>
        
    </div>
</body>
</html>
